<p>The HQ also features a rolling exhibit. 007 x SPYSCAPE has recently moved out, and a physical component of a new Batman x SPYSCAPE mobile augmented reality game has moved in. Batman x Skyscape can be played anywhere in the world, but, if you happen to be in NYC, the game will also take you through the exhibition. It gives you the immersive experience of actually working with Batman and the characters from that universe.</p>

<div class="customer-quote-block" style="padding-left:5%;padding-right:5%">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
