<p>The physical exhibits in New York use RF wristbands and NFC to maintain a personalised sense of reality throughout the game, producing an immersive magic that resonates with customers. But another powerful element of the HQ‚Äôs immersiveness comes from its use of picture recognition.</p>

<div class="customer-quote-block" style="padding-left:5%;padding-right:5%">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
